OL,3,CPark visitors warned after footage
OL,4,Cshows people crowding and stroking deer
OL,6,FPark visitors have been warned to stay
OL,7,Faway from deer after footage showed
OL,8,Fadults and children crowding the
OL,9,Fanimals.
OL,11,FThe warning from the Royal Parks comes
OL,12,Fafter footage shared on social media
OL,13,Fover the weekend showed a group of
OL,14,Fadults and children crowding around
OL,15,Fand stroking deer in Richmond Park,
OL,16,Fsouth-west London.
