OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784193509
OL,3,CPark visitors warned after footage
OL,4,Cshows people crowding and stroking deer
OL,6,FThe red and fallow deer are "wild,
OL,7,Fpowerful animals" and visitors should
OL,8,Falways stay at least 50 metres away,
OL,9,FRichmond Park manager Paul Richards
OL,10,Fstressed.
OL,12,FHe said: "We are shocked and extremely
OL,13,Fconcerned by footage shared on social
OL,14,Fmedia showing a group of adults and
OL,15,Fyoung children crowding around deer in
OL,16,FRichmond Park, with children seen
OL,17,Ftouching and stroking the animals.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@QO]tD@JOU
