OL,3,CPark visitors warned after footage
OL,4,Cshows people crowding and stroking deer
OL,6,F"This deeply irresponsible and highly
OL,7,Fdangerous behaviour will cause the
OL,8,Fdeer stress and create a serious risk
OL,9,Fof a tragic accident resulting in life-
OL,10,Fchanging injuries or, in the worst
OL,11,Fcase, a fatal incident."
OL,13,FRichmond Park covers 2,500 acres and
OL,14,Fis a haven for wildlife but the deer
OL,15,Fare "powerful" creatures who can be
OL,16,F"quick to react".
OL,18,FMr Richards said: "Although they may
OL,19,Fappear calm, they can react suddenly
OL,20,Fand aggressively if they feel
OL,21,Fthreatened.
