OL,3,CPark visitors warned after footage
OL,4,Cshows people crowding and stroking deer
OL,6,F"Stags can weigh more than 25 stone
OL,7,Fand run at speeds of up to 30 miles
OL,8,Fper hour, making them highly dangerous
OL,9,Fif visitors get too close.
OL,11,FParents and carers were urged to keep
OL,12,Fchildren "well away from the deer at
OL,13,Fall times" and to never allow them to
OL,14,Fapproach or interact with the animals.
OL,16,FHe added: "Visitors should always stay
OL,17,Fat least 50 metres away ` or further
OL,18,Fif the deer are moving ` and never
OL,19,Fapproach them for photographs or
OL,20,Fselfies.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JOUuD@JO]xD@KOU
