OL,3,CPark visitors warned after footage
OL,4,Cshows people crowding and stroking deer
OL,6,F"The deer are one of the park's most
OL,7,Ficonic and valued features.
OL,9,F"But please ` keep yourself, your
OL,10,Ffamilies, and others safe, by giving
OL,11,Fdeer the space they need."
